          <h1>Trokam needs your contribution!</h1>

          <p class="fs-5">You have several alternatives to donate to Trokam: a monthly
                          or a one-time contribution using traditional currencies or a
                          one-time contribution using cryptocurrencies.
          </p>
          &nbsp;<br/>

          <h2 id="monthly">Montly contributions</h2>

          <p class="fs-5">Set a montly contribution of &euro;1, &euro;3 or &euro;5 using Patreon.
                          Patreon provides a conversion to your local currency if possible.
          </p>
          <div class="mb-5">
            <a href="https://www.patreon.com/trokam" class="btn btn-success btn-lg px-4">Go to Trokam's Patreon page</a>
          </div>

          <p class="fs-5">Set a montly contribution of &euro;1, &euro;3 or &euro;5 using 'Buy Me a Coffee'.
          </p>
          <div class="mb-5">
            <a href="https://www.buymeacoffee.com/trokam" class="btn btn-success btn-lg px-4">Go to Trokam's Buy Me a Coffee page</a>
          </div>

          <p class="fs-5">Set a montly contribution of &euro;1, &euro;2 or any amount with Ko-Fi.
          </p>
          <div class="mb-5">
            <a href="https://ko-fi.com/trokam" class="btn btn-success btn-lg px-4">Go to Trokam's Ko-Fi page</a>
          </div>

          <p class="fs-5">Set a montly contribution of &euro;1 or higher using Stripe. Stripe gives
                          you several options as Apple Pay, Google Pay, iDEAL and credit cards. Stripe
                          provides a conversion to your local currency if possible.
                          <em>Go to 'Details' and select a different 'Qty' (Quantity) to change the amount.</em>
          </p>
          <div class="mb-5">
            <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/28o8xi6LTazUcyk4gh" class="btn btn-success btn-lg px-4">Go to Trokam's Stripe page</a>
          </div>

