          <p class="fs-5">Any donation to Trokam or Nicolas Slusarenko is voluntary
                          and is not a fee for any services, goods, or advantages.
                          By donating, you acknowledge that Trokam has the right to
                          use the money you donate in any lawful way and for any lawful
                          purpose. No obligation is to disclose the way and purpose to
                          any party unless applicable law requires it. Although Trokam
                          is built on free software, Trokam does not have any tax-exempt
                          status. Trokam is not a registered non-profit corporation in
                          any country. Your donation may or may not be tax-deductible;
                          please consult your tax advisor. Trokam will not publish your
                          name without your consent. Your donation is non-refundable.
